========================================================================
DESCRIPTION=============================================================
========================================================================

This is a C library to handle suffix array construction in a
minimalistic, while still setting up all structures needed to replace
any use of suffix trees.

NOTE: Not all functionality is implemented, and what is is not 
nessicarily implemented correctly.  This is under development software.

========================================================================
BUILD AND INSTALL=======================================================
========================================================================

make install

